<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>NodCord - Home</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/css/styles.css">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        header {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            position: relative;
        }
        .logo {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .logo img {
            height: 40px;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }
        nav {
            display: flex;
        }
        nav a {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            margin: 0 5px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }
        nav a:hover {
            background-color: #575757;
        }
        main {
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .section {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .section h2 {
            margin-top: 0;
        }
        .section p {
            font-size: 16px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="logo">
            <img src="/assets/img/logo.png" alt="NodCord Logo">
            <span>NodCord</span>
        </div>
        <nav>
            <a href="/">Home</a>
            <a href="/dashboard">Dashboard</a>
            <a href="/discord-members">Discord Members</a>
            <a href="/discord-servers">Discord Servers</a>
            <a href="/status">API Status</a>
            <a href="/info">Info</a>
            <a href="/docs">Documentation</a>
        </nav>
    </header>
    <main>
        <div class="section">
            <h1>Welcome to NodCord</h1>
            <p>
                NodCord is an integrated project combining a Node.js API with Express.js and a Discord bot. This project provides a comprehensive API and a functional Discord bot for various use cases.
            </p>
            <p>
                The API includes a Discord service that can be managed through controllers and routes. The Discord bot can also be controlled via the API.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>About the Bot</h2>
            <p>
                The NodCord Discord bot is designed to interact with your Discord servers, providing commands for managing roles, users, and more. It's integrated into the API for seamless management and configuration.
            </p>
        </div>
    </main>
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 NodCord. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>